items.content_text:
### Programming Languages / [Other](#other-1)

*   [PHPArkitect (⭐825)](https://github.com/phparkitect/arkitect) — PHPArkitect helps you to keep your PHP codebase coherent and solid, by permitting to add some architectural constraint check to your workflow.
